high_descs: Turn around to face the potato on the counter.
Pick up the rightmost potato from the counter.
Walk to the larger sink on the right.
Put the potato in the sink.
Move left to reach the potato on the counter.
Pick up the other potato from the counter.
Turn right to get back to the larger sink.
Put the potato next to the other potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two Potato in the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the potato.
Take the potato from the table.
Then turn around and go near the sink.
Put the potato into the sink.
Then turn around and go near the potato.
Take another potato from the table.
Then go near the sink.
Put the potato into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Collect the Potato and put it into the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the kitchen sink, stopping at the potato on the counter next to it.
Pick up the potato on the right from the counter.
Go to the sink.
Place the potato in the sink.
Return to the counter where you got the potato.
Pick up the other potato.
Go to the sink again.
Place the second potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place two Potato in a SinkBasin.
